WEBVTT

00:01:59.920 --> 00:02:01.586
All the way to school,

00:02:01.610 --> 00:02:04.526
and then all the way back
because I was sent home at once --

00:02:04.550 --> 00:02:05.858
(Laughter)

00:02:05.882 --> 00:02:09.989
I transformed into
a little brown rock star.

00:02:10.013 --> 00:02:11.552
(Laughter)

00:02:11.576 --> 00:02:14.551
I finally didn't care anymore
that I could not conform.

00:02:14.982 --> 00:02:17.680
That day, I was suddenly celebrating it.

00:02:18.770 --> 00:02:21.500
That day, instead of being invisible,

00:02:21.524 --> 00:02:23.318
I chose to be looked at,

00:02:24.206 --> 00:02:26.279
just by wearing something different.

00:02:27.136 --> 00:02:31.418
That day, I discovered
the power of what we wear.